{"tid":624604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尷尬！美斯生涯九次歐冠被淘汰出局均未取得進球","createTime":"2018-04-10T22:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T13:12:14.000Z","uid":27416,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"013dd62f088901dade5bb99f94c571077940c2c6","tid":624604,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"美斯職業生涯9次在歐冠比賽中被淘汰出局，在生死之戰中，美斯的進球數每次都是0。從2007年輸給曼聯開始，每次巴塞在歐冠被淘汰出局，美斯都沒能通過進球幫助球隊取勝。本賽季只要美斯不在場或者發揮不佳，巴塞別說取勝，就是收穫平局也是僥倖。今天的比賽除了開場給羅拔圖的傳球，美斯全場比賽發揮毫無亮點，羅馬很成功地限制住了美斯的發揮。<br />\n<br />\n正如《世界體育報》所說，巴塞球迷不得不接受這個悲傷的事實：沒有美斯，巴塞一無是處。"},{"pid":"af045b10973d8614391f72e19377f45920dff91a","tid":624604,"uid":25345,"like":47,"dislike":10,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T22:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔睇以為小花冇出埸<br />\n有小花咪一樣一無是處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得屁馬走<br />\n輸左又係隊友一無是處自己甩身 <br />\n上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c15ebcc1c626e1e791f696e49a3cd35ea25a06","tid":624604,"uid":1147,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af045b10973d8614391f72e19377f45920dff91a","tid":624604,"uid":25345,"like":47,"dislike":10,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T22:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔睇以為小花冇出埸<br />\n有小花咪一樣一無是處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得屁馬走<br />\n輸左又係隊友一無是處自己甩身 <br />\n上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T22:49:04.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇佢啲精華架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 半場等於個新類型球玉成季呀"},{"pid":"9175f52e8d419d1c09d94a9cc2f5890f226a557b","tid":624604,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16c15ebcc1c626e